Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:23.49,JoJo-Location,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(294,0)\fs20}— 1983: The Canary Islands, Off the Northwest African Coast —
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.42,0:00:32.83,JoJo-main,glasses,0000,0000,0000,,W-We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.83,0:00:37.22,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally pulled up the treasure chest \Nthat sank one hundred years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.22,0:00:39.02,JoJo-main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Careful now!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.02,0:00:42.64,JoJo-main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Keep calm! Just bring it this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.63,0:00:42.64,JoJo-overlap,glasses,0000,0000,0000,,I know! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.64,0:00:43.52,JoJo-main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Up we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.82,0:00:46.90,JoJo-main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it a bit long and narrow \Nto be a treasure chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.90,0:00:49.11,JoJo-main,glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're lifting it too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.15,0:00:52.16,JoJo-main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm putting it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:54.29,JoJo-main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:58.01,JoJo-main,glasses,0000,0000,0000,,All right! H-Hurry up and pry it open.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.01,0:00:59.78,JoJo-main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Th-This is bizarre.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:03.04,JoJo-main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,This box is locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.04,0:01:05.73,JoJo-main,glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell cares? Bust it open!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:07.97,JoJo-main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,Just hang on! There's something written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:11.92,JoJo-main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,D-I-O... DIO.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:13.23,JoJo-main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:15.67,JoJo-main,glasses,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell does it matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.67,0:01:17.54,JoJo-main,glasses,0000,0000,0000,,The sun's going to set soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:19.96,JoJo-main,glasshes,0000,0000,0000,,Once it gets dark, we won't \Nbe able to see anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.63,JoJo-main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.63,0:01:23.69,JoJo-main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll go get the blowtorch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.69,0:01:26.82,JoJo-main,glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Let's say hello to our treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:33.32,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,One day, an unmanned \Ncabin cruiser was spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.18,0:01:37.98,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,The boat was in perfect working order, \Nand there were no signs of an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.58,0:01:42.82,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,Aboard, there were only\N three half-full cups of coffee,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.82,0:01:44.24,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:50.70,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,On deck, a steel box, which had been\N opened with an acetylene torch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:52.69,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The box was empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.69,0:01:57.59,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,and strangely, it had two compartments, \Nas if designed to shelter something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.52,0:02:01.03,JoJo-internal/narrator,nar,0000,0000,0000,,It was thought to have contained treasure,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:04.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,but after a few months, it was forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:16.13,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro Kujo, 17 years old. \NHeight: 195 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:19.24,JoJo-top,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,His father is Japanese, and a jazz musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.97,0:02:23.57,JoJo-Location2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(294,0)}1987: Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.45,JoJo-top,,0000,0000,0000,,He's currently on tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:24.99,JoJo-top,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,His mother is an American of British descent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:29.00,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Jotaro is definitely my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:31.91,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, his friends at school call him "Jojo,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:35.81,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,derived from the "Jo" of Jotaro and the "jo" in Kujo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.53,0:02:37.89,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:39.80,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,S-So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.36,0:02:43.18,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,How many people did Jotaro kill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.18,0:02:47.42,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't tell me! I don't want to hear! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:48.07,JoJo-overlap,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, who said he killed anybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.57,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,He got into a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.57,0:02:53.92,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, the thugs he faced were \Narmed with nunchucks and knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:56.18,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,There were four, including a former boxer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:02:58.75,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,and between them, fifteen bones were broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:00.65,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,They all had their balls crushed, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.65,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, pardon my language...\N And they were sent to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.65,0:03:07.17,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, please make sure he learns his lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:08.41,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:10.65,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,But the problem is what happened after.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:12.34,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Could you copy this and pass it around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.29,JoJo-main,lady,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:15.67,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Your son is quite the oddball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.02,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Come in. We'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.02,0:03:22.26,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.64,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway, please take him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.64,0:03:26.75,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,What? He's being released already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.38,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can't keep him forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:34.02,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, ma'am, \Nyour Japanese is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:36.27,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you lived in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.27,0:03:37.57,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:39.29,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.29,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.73,0:03:43.34,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,We've had our hands full lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:46.75,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,There's even a waiting list for cells.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:48.77,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,Your son is just up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.54,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.83,JoJo-flashback,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, throw the ball to Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:03:58.09,JoJo-flashback,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.11,0:04:01.54,JoJo-flashback,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best at the sports meet tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:02.28,JoJo-flashback,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:03.84,JoJo-internal/narrator,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:07.05,Jojo-Entrance,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.81,JoJo-flashback,holly,0000,0000,0000,,We should celebrate.\N What would you like to eat today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:09.31,JoJo-flashback,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to eat your cooking, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:12.61,JoJo-internal/narrator,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro... Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:15.73,JoJo-internal/narrator,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro... Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.01,0:04:17.42,JoJo-internal/narrator,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.73,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.82,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so damn annoying, you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:25.20,JoJo-Bam,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(233,0)}Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:27.28,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:32.71,JoJo-MainTitle,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(237,0)}JoJo's {\c&H2E0FB2&}Bizarre Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:32.71,JoJo-MainTitle2,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1526,0)}Stardust Crusaders
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.96,JoJo-top,holly,0000,0000,0000,,He's actually a very sweet child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:36.56,JoJo-EpTitle,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,368)}Episode 1: The Man Possessed by an Evil Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.99,JoJo-top,holly,0000,0000,0000,,He's not capable of doing something so appalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:40.14,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't fall asleep, Kujo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.69,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,You're being released. Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.69,0:04:44.03,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,What part of "go home" don't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:53.70,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:55.98,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to leave here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:59.46,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I've been possessed by an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:02.40,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what he'll make me do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:06.45,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Even during the fight,\N it took all I had to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.63,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,So don't let me out of this cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:14.09,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud...\N See what I'm talking about, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:17.26,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying to release him, \Nbut he refuses to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:22.46,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive my asking, but is \Nyour son all right upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.05,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:27.07,JoJo-main,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Let us change cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.99,JoJo-main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,He's telling the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.99,0:05:31.03,JoJo-main,guy 1,0000,0000,0000,,There really is an evil spirit possessing him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:30.67,JoJo-overlap,guy 3,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.35,JoJo-main,guy 2,0000,0000,0000,,We won't do anything bad again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:34.60,JoJo-overlap,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough! Quiet down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.62,0:05:44.47,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:48.70,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,You've been locked up! \NHow'd you get that in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.52,0:05:52.91,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:54.43,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,It's the evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.94,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,The evil spirit brings things to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:58.97,JoJo-announcer,radio,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nokotta! Nokotta! Nokotta!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:02.60,JoJo-announcer,radio,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}He tosses him out of the ring! \NChiyonofuji wins all fourteen matches!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.97,0:06:02.60,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's listening to a boombox \Nand reading {\i1}Shonen Jump{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:05.02,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,H-How?! Th-This is a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.02,0:06:06.26,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a huge problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.77,0:06:06.82,JoJo-overlap,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.75,0:06:11.26,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,This might not be enough to \Nstop you from releasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.88,0:06:14.39,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you what a terror \Nmy evil spirit can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:19.09,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Just so you'll understand how \Ndangerous it could be to let me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.77,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,M-My gun! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.87,JoJo-overlap,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,W-We've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:40.23,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did you guys see \Nmy evil spirit just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:42.24,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.30,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,J-Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:00.53,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.53,0:07:02.57,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have possessed me recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.37,0:07:08.58,JoJo-internal/narrator,holly,0000,0000,0000,,His grandpa, Joseph, had strange powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:12.45,JoJo-internal/narrator,holly,0000,0000,0000,,B-But what's happening to my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.02,0:07:18.95,JoJo-Eyecatch,sign bot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(875,0)}Jotaro Kujo
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:25.27,JoJo-Location,warning,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(459,459)\b0\fs18}This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names \Nused in this program have no connection to any existing in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:25.38,JoJo-top,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.38,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, Papa! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.21,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly! Hey, outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.21,0:07:30.55,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.70,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:34.64,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:37.13,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,If my only daughter needs my help,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:41.12,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can be anywhere in the world within 24 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:43.35,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.13,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,She complained...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:49.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But I told Suzie it was a business \Ntrip for Joestar Real Estate Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:52.44,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly... Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.20,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Holly! Get off of me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:07:59.95,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:03.27,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,It's been forever since you've held me, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:04.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Look, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:08.25,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You're a 45-year-old woman. \NHow can you talk like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:11.00,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now you've done it! \NI'm going to tickle you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:12.84,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Tickle, tickle, tickle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:12.84,JoJo-overlap,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.51,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Take that and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.04,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you guys staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.35,JoJo-main,kid,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.35,JoJo-overlap,mom,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.73,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:24.85,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Holly, about Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:27.36,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You're certain he said "evil spirit"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.13,0:08:32.08,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... my dear Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:35.02,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The policemen said they couldn't see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.59,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,but I clearly saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:38.70,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,I saw a separate arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:40.51,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,And it grabbed the gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.51,0:08:44.00,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Others couldn't see it, but you could?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:45.21,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:48.27,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,So Jotaro says that he's \Nbeen possessed recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:50.25,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing strange has happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:56.35,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,No. But Jotaro says he won't leave\N the cell until he knows what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.88,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:09:00.14,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, my beloved daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:03.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I, Joseph Joestar, am here now,\N so there's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.57,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.49,0:09:11.82,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,First, I'd like to hurry
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,and see my grandson, Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.14,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,H-How terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.14,0:09:29.08,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,He's got more stuff again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.11,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,And it's violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:33.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something terrifying possessing him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:39.23,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,I-If anyone outside found out about this, \NI'd lose my job in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:43.10,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my grandson home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.10,0:09:44.43,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,"Grandson"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.19,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:49.58,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you can't go in any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.98,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Convince him from over here! It's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:53.33,JoJo-overlap,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. Step aside! Leave him to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:54.73,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,We can't be held responsible for this! Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:54.74,JoJo-overlap,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, you're in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.98,0:09:58.70,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro! It's your grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.32,0:10:01.24,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll be able to help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.57,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Please come out with your grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:14.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Get out. We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.65,0:10:16.76,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:18.79,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask you to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:23.47,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Help me? What the hell can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.35,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry you came all the way from New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:28.85,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,but there's no way you can help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:30.10,JoJo-Bang,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(320,0)}Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:35.29,JoJo-topinternal,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The pinky from my artificial left hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.29,0:10:37.80,JoJo-topinternal,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,When was it torn off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:41.05,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You see? Do you get it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.83,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.77,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:48.33,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You'll just shorten what \Nlittle life you have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.93,JoJo-topinternal,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,H-How can this be? I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:55.57,JoJo-topinternal,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It was able to deceive me right off the bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.47,0:11:00.96,JoJo-topinternal,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I know exactly\N what Jotaro's evil spirit is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.96,0:11:02.91,JoJo-topinternal,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But rather than explaining it with words,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:05.82,JoJo-topinternal,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,if he experiences the truth himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.28,JoJo-topinternal,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,he'll understand it much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:11.07,JoJo-topinternal,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,No, he needs to physically understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:13.23,JoJo-topinternal,,0000,0000,0000,,because of the dangers \Nhe'll face in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:17.26,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:21.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Egyptian friend \NI met three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:23.67,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:30.10,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Chase my grandson Jotaro out of this cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.04,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:35.24,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,He looks strong, but do you really \Nthink I'd let someone
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:38.63,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,chase me out of here just \Nbecause you told him to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.07,0:11:40.64,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:43.39,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm just gonna be even more stubborn
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.79,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and want to leave even less.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.92,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to get a bit violent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.92,0:11:50.98,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,But soon enough, \Nhe'll be so addled with pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.98,0:11:53.45,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,he'll be squealing, \N"Please get me out of here."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.45,0:11:54.89,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.32,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Papa, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.02,JoJo-main,cop,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, we can't have you—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:59.18,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.18,0:12:00.15,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.05,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:20.36,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:23.77,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol also has a so-called "evil spirit."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.77,0:12:26.51,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,An evil spirit that Avdol can control freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:28.14,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The evil spirit's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Magician's Red!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.07,0:12:41.62,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's hot! Fire! I'm burning!\N My arms are burning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.82,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is this evil spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:47.60,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Kujo's plastered himself\N against the wall and won't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.60,0:12:48.58,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.81,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,B-But isn't it getting sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.81,0:12:53.30,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,How is it that hot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.46,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,That's insane! It's way too hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:06.22,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,There it is! It's finally shown itself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:10.72,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And the fact that it's so clearly \Nvisible means it's very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.97,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:21.72,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he's able to \Nmake it manifest this clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:24.39,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you have an evil spirit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:28.37,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,And Grandpa, the identity of the evil spirit...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.52,0:13:29.95,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I know it, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:31.12,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.45,0:13:34.80,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,you asked me to get your \Ngrandson out of the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:37.08,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning on holding back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:41.03,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,but considering its unexpected power,\None misstep and we'll be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.72,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:48.16,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,If you still insist that I get him out, \NI'll have to get violent enough
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:50.60,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,to send your grandson to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:52.85,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine. Give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.35,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.11,0:13:58.13,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Red Bind!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:00.41,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:07.72,JoJo-main,cop,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:10.33,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.33,0:14:13.22,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Papa! What are you doing to Jotaro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.71,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Holly, be a good girl and keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:17.40,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.40,0:14:19.05,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.06,0:14:22.06,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,The evil spirit's withdrawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:24.28,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,If the heat is restricting your breathing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,your evil spirit will weaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:28.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I shall reveal its identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:31.30,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It may seem like an evil spirit, but it is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.06,0:14:34.60,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro! What you believed to be an evil spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:38.81,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,is a powerful vision, \Ncreated from your own life energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:44.07,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Because it appears next to you,\N that vision is called...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:45.61,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.77,JoJo-Bam2,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.18,JoJo-internal/narrator,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,A Stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.68,0:14:50.53,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,As told in Aesop's fable,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:54.33,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,the cold wind only made the \Ntraveler pull his coat on tight,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:56.52,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,but the heat made him admit defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:14:59.16,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come out \Nof your cage now, Jojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.92,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.17,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I won't leave
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:08.26,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,is because I keep harming \Nothers without realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.98,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, it interests me that \Nyou have an evil spirit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.52,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,But if you keep going,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.36,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,you're gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:25.19,JoJo-main,cop b,0000,0000,0000,,He broke the toilet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.46,JoJo-main,cop a,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's destruction of property!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.79,0:15:32.41,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.21,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.21,0:15:38.32,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say I didn't warn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:53.97,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.47,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you suddenly turn your back on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.72,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Turn and face me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.27,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Joestar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:03.47,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,\N I've gotten him out of his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:04.52,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.79,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you let me win?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.04,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.44,0:16:21.98,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I truly did plan to send you to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.67,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,but I did not expect such power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:28.84,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,If I hadn't stopped this steel rod,\N what were you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.61,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,My Stand is Magician's Red.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:36.22,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,It could melt a steel rod\N like this in the air with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:39.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol has the same power as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:44.18,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to stay in that cell
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.18,0:16:46.56,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,to research your evil spirit any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.99,JoJo-Eyecatch3,sign top,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(501,0)}Magician's Red
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.01,0:16:52.99,JoJo-Eyecatch2,sign bot,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1021,0)}Mohammed Avdol
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.99,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:01.00,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro finally came out of his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:03.56,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying, you bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.59,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.58,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:09.75,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you call your \Nown mother a bitch, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.02,0:17:12.94,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And, Holly, stop smiling\N after he just called you that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.94,0:17:13.88,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.34,0:17:16.50,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, there's one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:19.10,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask you about\N one thing I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:24.97,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you know about my evil spirit—\N no, my Stand or whatever?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:26.47,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:29.11,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:32.61,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I came all the way from \NNew York to explain that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.91,0:17:37.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But in order to explain it,\N I must start at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:40.12,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This has to do with the Joestar family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.75,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,First, take a look at these pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.50,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:52.65,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,That's a hundred-year-old coffin \Npulled up from the Atlantic Ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.73,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,off the African coast four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.76,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Coffin?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:58.68,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,After I obtained and researched it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:03.53,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I found out that it was on the \Nboat where my grandfather,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:07.60,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the man four generations before you,\N Jonathan Joestar, died.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:12.15,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It was apparently empty \Nwhen they discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.59,0:18:15.36,JoJo-main,jospeh,0000,0000,0000,,But I know exactly what was inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:18.61,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol and I are trying to \Nlocate him as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:20.74,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Him? Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.74,0:18:23.79,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You're making it sound like \Nthere was a person in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:27.87,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you call something lost \Nat sea for a hundred years "him"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:30.04,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He is evil incarnate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.43,0:18:32.25,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,His name is DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.98,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He has awakened from his hundred-year sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:38.55,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,We are fated to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.02,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,What was that, Jotaro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:46.43,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a face like this \Nhas nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.16,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,This face means,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:51.06,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,"That was so stupid, I don't \Nknow what to say," Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.06,0:18:53.33,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,G-Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.79,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.79,0:18:58.04,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, \Nbut you're sure full of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:01.76,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,And Old Man, do you expect \Nme to hear such a crazy story
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.76,0:19:04.24,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and just say, "Oh, I see," and believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:13.00,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,But is it not a fact that our \Nevil spirits are crazy, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:15.25,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:17.92,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon, you'll have no choice but to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:23.26,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,If you ask me why I know of DIO's existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:25.55,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,and why I'm after him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:28.17,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.17,0:19:30.05,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, about a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.05,0:19:35.36,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I also suddenly obtained an evil spirit,\N or rather, the power of a Stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:36.65,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:38.19,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man, what did you—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:40.99,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I shall show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,This is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:44.55,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,my Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:46.47,JoJo-Bang,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H40DED5&}Crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.61,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:56.55,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,The thorns that came from my hand?\N This is my Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:00.80,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Its power is to take spirit photos of \Nvisions I captured from far-off places!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:05.55,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Though I have to smash and destroy a \N30,000 yen camera every time I do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:08.56,JoJo-main,waitor,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.56,0:20:10.75,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,We're fine. Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.75,0:20:11.81,JoJo-main,waitor,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:15.42,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The vision that's going to \Nappear in this picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.42,0:20:16.32,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.80,0:20:19.62,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,will be what determines your fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:20.82,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:26.96,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro, Holly, have either of you ever \Nlooked carefully at the back of your necks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:28.95,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.50,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,You've probably never taken a close look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:37.63,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,But right around the base of my neck, \Nthere is a star-shaped birthmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.38,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask again. What the hell does all this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.74,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I asked my mother about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:49.26,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,and she said that my father,\N who died when I was young, also had it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:54.38,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, those of the Joestar \Nbloodline all have this birthmark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:55.85,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Old Man,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.36,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you what's going \Nto show up on that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:01.95,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It is our destiny, as yet undiscovered!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:03.10,JoJo-overlap,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.95,0:21:06.16,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, just show me what's on it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:13.13,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:16.19,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,He is always the one who \Nshows up in my spirit photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.19,0:21:18.67,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And on the back of his neck...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.13,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,From this bastard's neck down,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,is the body of my grandfather, \NJonathan Joestar,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.15,0:21:26.29,JoJo-Rumble,sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:26.30,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,which that bastard has taken over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:31.77,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,A hundred years ago,\N an incident occurred in the Atlantic Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:35.34,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I only know what I heard \Nfrom my grandmother, Erina,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.34,0:21:39.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,but DIO took over the body of \Nmy grandfather and survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.89,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And this much is certain:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.89,0:21:46.99,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,He is currently hiding somewhere \Nin the world, plotting something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:49.46,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,It's been four years since he came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.46,0:21:51.81,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,The reason my spirit photos and your evil spirits
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:54.88,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,all began manifesting in this past year...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.88,0:21:57.00,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,is most likely DIO!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:22:01.25,JoJo-top,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,In the wider world, our gifts \Nare considered psychic powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.68,0:22:04.31,JoJo-top,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I've had my Stand since birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:07.20,JoJo-top,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,but your powers are bound to DIO's body...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:11.26,JoJo-top,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Jonathan's body,\N by invisible threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.75,0:22:14.59,JoJo-top,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,All we can say now is that DIO's \Nexistence is what brought forth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.59,0:22:17.27,JoJo-top,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,the powers that were dormant within you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:22.52,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Avdol, from this photo, \Ncan you tell where he is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:27.60,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot. There's hardly any background visible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:29.00,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.37,0:22:31.41,JoJo-main,avdol,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:32.79,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Please. Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.29,0:22:35.93,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.93,0:22:38.53,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for bringing all this up so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.53,0:22:39.98,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.98,0:22:40.92,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:44.02,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,I will be staying in Japan for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.02,0:22:46.09,JoJo-main,joseph,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be staying at your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.33,0:22:47.73,JoJo-top,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.73,0:22:49.47,JoJo-top,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Jotaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.18,0:23:04.57,JoJo-main,Dio,0000,0000,0000,,It happened again...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.85,0:23:10.40,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, it felt as though \Nsomeone was watching me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:13.95,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Jonathan's descendants, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.95,0:23:18.96,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,This body must be sending out some \Nkind of soul signal to his descendants.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.85,0:23:23.31,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. This might be called fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:25.70,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,A fate I must be rid of,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.70,0:23:27.62,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,a destiny I must erase.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.34,0:23:31.03,JoJo-main,dio,0000,0000,0000,,I have already made my move.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:37.02,JoJo-Preview,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.73,0:23:37.02,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Jotaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:39.37,JoJo-main,holly,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a goodbye kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.15,JoJo-main,jotaro,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:41.97,JoJo-overlap,nori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Noriaki Kakyoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.97,0:23:44.78,JoJo-main,nori,0000,0000,0000,,I just transferred here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.77,0:23:46.28,JoJo-overlap,person,0000,0000,0000,,Does this look like a pen to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.28,0:23:48.80,JoJo-main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,The loser is the evil one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:50.02,JoJo-NextTitle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.03,0:23:50.02,JoJo-NextTitle2,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Who Will Be the Judge!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.80,0:23:50.30,JoJo-main,someone,0000,0000,0000,,The one who'll be the judge is...
